### Querying Data

You can use the Drizzle query builder for type-safe SQL:

```typescript
const users = await db.select().from(user).where(eq(user.id, 1));
```
 [(1)](https://orm.drizzle.team/docs/get-started-postgresql)  [(2)](https://orm.drizzle.team) 

